<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فِي الْأَصَح عِنْد الْأَكْثَرين<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لعدم ضبط ناره وَمُقَابل الْأَصَح يَصح<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَا يَصح<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
